com.myscript.atk.itc

Interface IStrokeUserParamsFactory


  • public interface IStrokeUserParamsFactory
    This interface defines a stroke user parameters factory as seen by the interactive text component. This interface must be implemented by the application that wants to make use of user parameters.

    • Method Summary
